description.raw:
Current gazebo package depends on libavcodec53. This libavcode53[libavcodec53 package](http://packages.ubuntu.com/oneiric/amd64/libavcodec53/filelist) seems to provide the same files that ones provided by libavcodec53-extra [libavcodec53-extra](http://packages.ubuntu.com/oneiric/amd64/libavcodec-extra-53/filelist). One blocks the other so only one can be installed in the system at the same time.

@nkoenig found that when trying to install new gazebo version, apt ask him to uninstall his  libavcodec-extra-53 package to install gazebo.

This pull request makes gazebo to depend on one of this two options.

